Riot police unleashed tear gas to disperse the crowds, and by early on Friday evening, the area was deserted with haphazard roadblocks made of railings and rubbish bins littered about.<\/p>\r\n\r\n

"The problem isn't about masking or not," said Calvin Chan, a 20-year-old demonstrator, donning a surgical mask. <\/p>\r\n\r\n

